      "role": "user",
      "content": "no its not just signal strength.. i mean the name is literally telling me they are watching me. it's way too specific to be a coincidence. plus it only peaks when i'm moving around. do you think they could be using something like way more advanced sensors or signal triangulation to track where im standing in the house?",
